      <h1 class='title'>Public Interest Disclosure Act</h1>
    </div>
    <div class='commons-written-statements-sitting' id='content'>
      
      <cite class='section'>HC Deb 27 October 2003 vol 412 c105WS</cite>
      <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_105ws' title='Col. 105WS &mdash; HC Deb 27 October 2003 vol 412 c105WS' name='column_105ws' href='#column_105ws' rel='bookmark'>105WS</a>
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S6CV0412P0-05238'>
        <a name='S6CV0412P0_20031027_CWS2_530'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-colin-pickthall' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0412P0_20031027_CWS2_530' title='Link to this speech by Mr Colin Pickthall' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-colin-pickthall" title="Mr Colin Pickthall">Mr. Pickthall</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para" id="S6CV0412P0-05238">To ask the Secretary of State for Health if he will make a statement on his Department's obligations under the <a href="/acts/public-interest-disclosure-act-1998">Public Interest Disclosure Act 1998</a>; how many complaints were made concerning his Department in the last 12 months; and how long it took to resolve each complaint. [132324]</p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S6CV0412P0-05239'>
        <a name='S6CV0412P0_20031027_CWS2_531'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/ms-rosie-winterton' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0412P0_20031027_CWS2_531' title='Link to this speech by Ms Rosie Winterton' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/ms-rosie-winterton" title="Ms Rosie Winterton">Ms Rosie Winterton</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para" id="S6CV0412P0-05239"> <span class="italic">[holding answer 16 October 2003]:</span> The Department has no record of any complaints under the <a href="/acts/public-interest-disclosure-act-1998">Public Interest Disclosure Act 1998</a>.</p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
